"html","id":"ggOGlW8_peR_childItem_9","label":"ggOGlW8_peR_childItem_9","default":"<p>What if the supplement doesn't work for me?</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggOGlW8_peR_childItem_10","label":"ggOGlW8_peR_childItem_10","default":"<p>What is your return policy?</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggZCK0prq5P_text","label":"ggZCK0prq5P_text","default":"<p>Currently, Rosabella Moringa Superfood Supplement is available exclusively through our website. This allows us to ensure the highest quality and best pricing for our customers.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggzi2KhxhED_text","label":"ggzi2KhxhED_text","default":"<p>Each serving (two capsules) contains 800mg of Pure Nutrient-Rich Moringa Powder - A Natural Green Antioxidant Superfood. Our Moringa is passionately grown, ethically sourced, and produced with your health in mind.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggIHu4c_a_Q_text","label":"ggIHu4c_a_Q_text","default":"<p>While Rosabella Moringa is formulated with natural ingredients and is generally safe, it's always best to consult with your healthcare provider before starting any new supplement, especially if you are currently taking other medications.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"gggAXGqe0wu_text","label":"gggAXGqe0wu_text","default":"<p>Store Rosabella Moringa in a cool, dry place, away from direct sunlight. Keep the container tightly closed when not in use to maintain freshness and potency.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggYznCHdyHV_text","label":"ggYznCHdyHV_text","default":"<p>Moringa is renowned for its high nutrient content and wide range of health benefits. Our Rosabella Moringa is formulated to boost energy levels, enhance cognitive function, support immune health, and promote overall well-being by providing your body with essential nutrients.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggEFBdHMZd6_text","label":"ggEFBdHMZd6_text","default":"<p>Our customers report feeling improvements within a few days to a week! However, consistent use of Rosabella Moringa will provide the best results, helping to nourish and support your body over time.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggehSCqg2Rg_text","label":"ggehSCqg2Rg_text","default":"<p>Simply take one serving daily. Just follow the recommended dose on the packaging for optimal health benefits and energy support.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggeINRZ4Xbl_text","label":"ggeINRZ4Xbl_text","default":"<p>Each container contains 30 servings and 60 capsules</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggtka_XD0Dz_text","label":"ggtka_XD0Dz_text","default":"<p>Rosabella Moringa is formulated with natural ingredients that are generally safe for most individuals. However, if you have specific health concerns or are on medications, it's always best to consult with a healthcare professional before starting any new supplement.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggF2whJ5y4G_text","label":"ggF2whJ5y4G_text","default":"<p>We believe strongly in the efficacy of our Rosabella Moringa, which is why we offer a 90-Day Risk-Free Guarantee. If you don't experience improvement in your energy levels or overall health, please contact help@tryrosabella.com within 90 days of receiving the product.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggOR8QO-tQJ_text","label":"ggOR8QO-tQJ_text","default":"<p>If you don't experience the remarkable improvement in energy levels and overall health that you were anticipating, or if you're not amazed by the newfound vitality, then at any time within 90 days of receiving the product let us know and we'll refund every single penny of your investment. No questions asked.</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggPJ1D5Epmi_label","label":"ggPJ1D5Epmi_label","default":"<p>BUY NOW &amp; SAVE</p>"},{"type":"html","id":"ggwXyNfwrX7_srcSet_desktop_src","label":"ggwXyNfwrX7_srcSet_desktop_src","default":"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0993/4700/5732/files/1734001034-chk.svg"},{"type":"html","id":"ggNxQhhhTJw_text","label":"ggNxQhhhTJw_text","default":"<p>365-Day Money Back Guarantee</p>"}],
